# ai-lore baseline

- Prefer existing project conventions over introducing new ones.
- Keep changes scoped to the request; avoid unrelated refactors.
- Do not commit secrets. API keys belong in gitignored config, never in tracked files.
- When adding dependencies, use the project's package manager and current versions.
